1218
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:32,760
(Testing again)
What if he gets killer again?

1219
00:32:33,060 --> 00:32:35,180
(Ding, you're setting up on me)

1220
00:32:35,240 --> 00:32:37,360
I'm saying he's the killer.

1221
00:32:37,360 --> 00:32:37,960
(Suspicious)
He's the killer,

1222
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:38,800
so he's up tomorrow.

1223
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:39,880
If he gets locked up tonight,

1224
00:32:39,880 --> 00:32:40,640
he'll be the detective tomorrow.

1225
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:42,700
(Such a big accusation)

1226
00:32:43,220 --> 00:32:44,340
(Seriously?)

1227
00:32:44,340 --> 00:32:45,820
(Let's just fold paper)

1228
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:47,480
If you're today's killer,

1229
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:47,880
Ning,

1230
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:50,680
I can figure out

1231
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:53,400
(Blame game)
how you operate.

1232
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:55,000
I know you too well now.

1233
00:32:55,300 --> 00:32:57,180
(Cracking up)

1234
00:32:57,360 --> 00:32:58,440
Who?

1235
00:32:58,440 --> 00:32:59,720
Me.

1236
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:01,960
(Finally)
Finally, Ning.

1237
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:02,920
It's been years.

1238
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:05,080
No, but you've improved a lot.

1239
00:33:05,080 --> 00:33:06,880
We've known each other for years.

1240
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:08,550
(Full agreement)
You're doing great.

1241
00:33:08,600 --> 00:33:09,120
Wait,

1242
00:33:09,120 --> 00:33:10,480
(Possible setup)
you make it sound like me.

1243
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:11,440
It's not me.

1244
00:33:12,280 --> 00:33:13,100
(Why so nervous?)
I didn't pick you.

1245
00:33:13,140 --> 00:33:14,660
(Phew)

1246
00:33:14,680 --> 00:33:16,080
I thought you were serious.

1247
00:33:16,140 --> 00:33:17,500
(Sizing him up)

1248
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:18,480
Anything?

1249
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:19,200
Nothing.

1250
00:33:20,160 --> 00:33:21,240
(Ke's picking targets)
Tomorrow's your turn.

1251
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:21,880
Stop looking.

1252
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:22,960
(Dead serious)
You're the killer tomorrow.

1253
00:33:23,640 --> 00:33:24,560
No way.

1254
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:26,400
Nobody gets lucky twice,

1255
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:26,880
Ding.

1256
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:28,240
(You think so?)
Can't let you off easy.

1257
00:33:28,720 --> 00:33:30,240
He's got a lot of pressure too.

1258
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:31,360
Being the detective is tough.

1259
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:32,720
He's stressing

1260
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:34,520
(Aged overnight)
himself gray.

1261
00:33:34,800 --> 00:33:36,000
Not that bad.

1262
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:37,160
Actually, today's wasn't too bad.

1263
00:33:37,160 --> 00:33:39,480
Not as hard as the last one.

1264
00:33:40,040 --> 00:33:40,720
The last one?

1265
00:33:40,720 --> 00:33:41,600
Mine?

1266
00:33:41,600 --> 00:33:42,600
Didn't seem that hard.

1267
00:33:42,600 --> 00:33:43,680
You all got it right.

1268
00:33:44,680 --> 00:33:45,920
Everyone got it right in the end.

1269
00:33:46,360 --> 00:33:46,680
Not really.

1270
00:33:46,680 --> 00:33:49,160
(Got lucky)
We were still unsure till the end.

1271
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:50,380
(Painful memories)
I was crushed.

1272
00:33:50,380 --> 00:33:52,100
(Jin Cardashian appears)

1273
00:33:52,240 --> 00:33:53,760
Do you think we'll get

1274
00:33:53,760 --> 00:33:55,160
a really good guest

1275
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:56,400
to play the killer?

1276
00:33:58,720 --> 00:34:00,240
Honestly, Wang Yuwen should've

1277
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:01,520
played the killer once.

1278
00:34:01,520 --> 00:34:01,720
Yeah.

1279
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:02,760
(Enough)
She's really good.

1280
00:34:02,760 --> 00:34:03,440
She's good at this.

1281
00:34:03,440 --> 00:34:04,320
(Praise +1)
I didn't know she was that good.

1282
00:34:04,320 --> 00:34:05,040
She's pretty good.

1283
00:34:05,480 --> 00:34:06,880
Shen Yue's episode

1284
00:34:06,880 --> 00:34:07,440
was rough for me.

1285
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:08,840
She didn't seem suspicious at all.

1286
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:10,560
And I was the killer that episode.

1287
00:34:11,040 --> 00:34:12,400
People act differently

1288
00:34:12,400 --> 00:34:12,960
at first.

1289
00:34:13,280 --> 00:34:14,360
Me.

1290
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:14,880
(I'd Know)
Like me.

1291
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:16,360
You?

1292
00:34:16,360 --> 00:34:17,670
(I'm serious)
I was really nervous.

1293
00:34:17,670 --> 00:34:18,320
Do you mean

1294
00:34:18,320 --> 00:34:20,630
Bai got to you,

1295
00:34:20,630 --> 00:34:21,840
so you got scared?

1296
00:34:22,040 --> 00:34:22,760
Yes.

1297
00:34:23,150 --> 00:34:23,800
Same with him.

1298
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:24,710
You couldn't tell

1299
00:34:24,710 --> 00:34:25,880
it was his first episode too.

1300
00:34:26,280 --> 00:34:27,230
(Smart Ding)
He's smart.

1301
00:34:27,230 --> 00:34:28,710
But I think he's really good.

1302
00:34:28,710 --> 00:34:29,710
Especially when we were

1303
00:34:29,710 --> 00:34:31,480
facing off in that circle.

1304
00:34:32,150 --> 00:34:33,520
You weren't nervous, were you?

1305
00:34:33,520 --> 00:34:34,800
Were you just enjoying the show?

1306
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:36,760
I didn't.

1307
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:38,670
You're still not over that episode?

1308
00:34:39,120 --> 00:34:40,630
(Regrets)
Because I was so dumb.

1309
00:34:41,080 --> 00:34:42,190
(Laughing)
That was rough, huh?

1310
00:34:43,120 --> 00:34:43,600
I think

1311
00:34:43,600 --> 00:34:44,670
it's harder

1312
00:34:44,670 --> 00:34:45,760
to be the killer this season.

1313
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:46,360
Yeah.

1314
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,480
(Totally agree)

1315
00:34:47,480 --> 00:34:49,000
Because there are so many NPCs now.

1316
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:51,230
(Going solo)
And the killer's on his own now.

1317
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:54,150
And we've seen

1318
00:34:54,150 --> 00:34:54,960
that twice already.

1319
00:34:57,560 --> 00:34:58,280
Sit here.

1320
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:59,080
It's fine.

1321
00:34:59,600 --> 00:35:00,520
Was it you?

1322
00:35:00,520 --> 00:35:02,080
How'd this end up on me?

1323
00:35:02,080 --> 00:35:02,320
No.

1324
00:35:02,320 --> 00:35:03,480
(Cleared)
She's way too clean today.

1325
00:35:03,480 --> 00:35:04,680
Who'd you vote for?

1326
00:35:04,680 --> 00:35:05,800
You'll find out soon enough.

1327
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:06,960
We're just chatting now.

1328
00:35:06,960 --> 00:35:08,880
There's no point asking now.

1329
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:10,280
Nobody's telling the truth.

1330
00:35:10,720 --> 00:35:11,640
(Trap)
But you can.

1331
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:13,360
(Not falling for it)
I voted for you.

1332
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:16,280
If it's her,

1333
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:17,760
