1334
00:35:17,760 --> 00:35:19,480
We'd look so dumb.

1335
00:35:20,080 --> 00:35:22,000
We all cleared her from the start.

1336
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:26,400
(Preview)
Give me half.

1337
00:35:26,560 --> 00:35:27,040
(Easygoing Ding)
Sure.

1338
00:35:27,040 --> 00:35:29,400
Half.

1339
00:35:29,720 --> 00:35:30,800
(Solo mission)
I actually got nothing

1340
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:31,560
in that hallway.

1341
00:35:31,560 --> 00:35:32,840
Then why were you screaming?

1342
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:33,560
(Even He's scared)
I was scared.

1343
00:35:33,560 --> 00:35:35,360
(Asking for more)
Zhang Linghe wants it scarier.

1344
00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:36,320
Even if no one was there,

1345
00:35:36,320 --> 00:35:38,000
I'd still be screaming.

1346
00:35:38,200 --> 00:35:39,160
Were you scared, Ning?

1347
00:35:39,160 --> 00:35:39,920
(Faking it)
I was terrified.

1348
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:41,080
Did you hear me

1349
00:35:41,080 --> 00:35:41,720
yelling for you?

1350
00:35:41,720 --> 00:35:42,120
No.

1351
00:35:42,400 --> 00:35:43,560
(Calling Jin first)
I yelled, "Jin Jing!"

1352
00:35:43,560 --> 00:35:44,280
She went, "Yeah?"

1353
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:45,980
(Evil mode activated)
I'll scare you to death.

1354
00:35:46,220 --> 00:35:47,140
(Getting ready to rappel)

1355
00:35:47,160 --> 00:35:48,760
You look good.

1356
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:50,640
Zhou Keyu looks like a pro.

1357
00:35:50,640 --> 00:35:51,900
(Perfect fit)

1358
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:53,120
Why do you look so pro?

1359
00:35:53,120 --> 00:35:54,580
Feels like this is my job.

1360
00:35:54,620 --> 00:35:55,560
(Epic shoot)
Let's do it.

1361
00:35:55,560 --> 00:35:56,280
Okay.

1362
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:58,200
Three, two, one, go!

1363
00:36:05,580 --> 00:36:06,500
(Gun-and-Baton Bros)

1364
00:36:06,860 --> 00:36:07,700
(Cool Sisters)

1365
00:36:08,060 --> 00:36:08,840
(Crossbow Duo)

1366
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:10,760
